data.title: Archduchess Elisabeth Franziska of Austria
data.meta_description: Archduchess Elisabeth Franziska Maria of Austria was born in Ofen (Buda), Hungary. She was the daughter of Palatine Joseph of Hungary (1776–1847) and his third wife Maria Dorothea of Württemberg (1797–1855).
